kpi_info.title: CS Voice + PS Multi RAB attempts
kpi_info.use: The number of RAB setup attemps the result of which would be a multi-RAB combination "CS AMR + PS NRT". Updated when CN requests the Multi-RAB combination to be set up. This is the case when a PS/CS RAB already exists and a CS/PS RAB is set up in addition to it (for the same RRC connection).
